一個問題，最後簡左馬灣"},{"pid":"5790905ef23015fe23caf295053095f9cadbef40","tid":1104864,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95b50b719c4a5d37553626f33cead1c105e4f73b","tid":1104864,"uid":158356,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"深井再入d 青龍頭啦<br />\n環境仲好，背山面海<br />\n有個盤做緊 6月到可以起貨<br />\n已經有人買緊<br />\n<br />\n利申：工程狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"逸瓏？青頭扮荃灣西"},{"pid":"e581ce351c7c3e656ac6b18cca3dae53d25f1743","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7509508f520f7845b8a9a6d4566720c386146567","tid":1104864,"uid":87555,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"馬灣以前果陣入去好少人巴士船都好平<br />\n而家真係兩個世界<br />\n又不停加價<br />\n架架車都滿<br />\n<br />\n深井上屯公又係大鑊<br />\n不過就真係得依兩個揀咪深井囉<br />\n起碼多啲嘢食丫<br />\n又唔洗比珀麗還客運揸住個春袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:00:33.000Z","msg":"我見而家出青衣$7荃灣葵芳就$10(居民)，想知前幾年係幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />升得好勁？"},{"pid":"5032f4cd2097a5e21b0f561de26e03e2a766cd83","tid":1104864,"uid":245059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:01:20.000Z","msg":"碧堤車位一百萬鬆啲 <br />\n租應該大約2500左右"},{"pid":"cf44434f38d3ee310388d52f52219913b5e3cf17","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b50b719c4a5d37553626f33cead1c105e4f73b","tid":1104864,"uid":158356,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"深井再入d 青龍頭啦<br />\n環境仲好，背山面海<br />\n有個盤做緊 6月到可以起貨<br />\n已經有人買緊<br />\n<br />\n利申：工程狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打意見先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但個人覺得青龍頭就有點兒入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df05a9df1444cbbd1af9c8f8441a3c58250e372","tid":1104864,"uid":37757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf44434f38d3ee310388d52f52219913b5e3cf17","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b50b719c4a5d37553626f33cead1c105e4f73b","tid":1104864,"uid":158356,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"深井再入d 青龍頭啦<br />\n環境仲好，背山面海<br />\n有個盤做緊 6月到可以起貨<br />\n已經有人買緊<br />\n<br />\n利申：工程狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打意見先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但個人覺得青龍頭就有點兒入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:03:19.000Z","msg":"青龍頭當你坐車咪又係多個彎位<br />\n係就食野少啲落樓下<br />\n但係住深井青龍頭咪又係為左靜<br />\n到時都係出去食/自己煮多"},{"pid":"7c54fb34fe1a6bb7dd3f9695d28701386a5514cf","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02bdfb29e6aeb0879caa04b0d56774f498a94517","tid":1104864,"uid":187484,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"我同你有過同一個問題，最後簡左馬灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:04:09.000Z","msg":"馬灣呎價相對再碧瑅同浪翠三四期平啲，真係幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打入咗去住之後感覺如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646de51c3aa951befe51a82bf4d9e588c5215a6c","tid":1104864,"uid":187484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c54fb34fe1a6bb7dd3f9695d28701386a5514cf","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02bdfb29e6aeb0879caa04b0d56774f498a94517","tid":1104864,"uid":187484,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"我同你有過同一個問題，最後簡左馬灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:04:09.000Z","msg":"馬灣呎價相對再碧瑅同浪翠三四期平啲，真係幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打入咗去住之後感覺如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"其實我仲未入住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡馬灣係因為可以坐船番中環，同埋佢d shuttle bus 好密。最重要係我未有能力養埋車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9030ab8a6c60960a064f60c1b83ec0e9fe39848","tid":1104864,"uid":62792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"住過馬灣二年,入面無乜野食,仲要唔太好食,星期六日假期果啲全個馬灣好似旺角咁多人<br />\n平日就真係夠晒靜"},{"pid":"27f0c3d6a9aae459e9d5588752cedcf6e850a7ae","tid":1104864,"uid":248276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"之前住荃灣,即將搬入碧堤,屋宛外觀幾好。環境同空氣都好唔錯,返工搭巴士去中環仲快過荃灣搭930.<br />\n尺價仲要平荃灣兩成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2be0bf833269349f8357cf117577088046ec09","tid":1104864,"uid":42395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"想問問 962b 出港島係深井上有冇位坐，thx"},{"pid":"4e8d961b27ad46936932be8ca850c5f48e4ecc50","tid":1104864,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c2be0bf833269349f8357cf117577088046ec09","tid":1104864,"uid":42395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"想問問 962b 出港島係深井上有冇位坐，thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"八點前上車實有"},{"pid":"f68684aea7d2b448bb6a7c0c459420f30879835d","tid":1104864,"uid":17474,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50adaea540dbd3bbac0139a2d7de6844187cac8a","tid":1104864,"uid":121364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"我揀深井<br />\n住咗浪翠園四五年，開頭租一期，之後上車買咗四期<br />\n住咗幾年，啱啱換樓，將會搬過碧堤半島<br />\n<br />\n碧堤位置好啲，但相比浪翠園就會遇到一啲內地人住客。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"大陸狗就大陸狗 <br />\n內乜地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0fdff852563c4c82586b3ad247cb4929bb6b44","tid":1104864,"uid":160102,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"住緊浪翠，之前係荃灣人，我估巴打你都同我一樣都係貪平先考慮馬灣或深井。<br />\n我買嗰時柏麗無哂六百樓下，無辦法下揀左深井，呀屌你又唔差喎，交通其實可接受，係放工時間巴士有時時間唔準同無位坐。<br />\n食野多數自己煮，百佳惠康佳寶全齊，街市就荃灣買完先番屋企，但要去深井村食野都大把選擇。<br />\nso far可接受，同埋你留意下，深井無野大陸佬，南亞佬，一般個個街坊都好有禮貌"},{"pid":"298720b6f4d18d940c62962c13ce5d0a235172bf","tid":1104864,"uid":49302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"兩邊都係長期號輸個市...巴打唔好咁衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a074955ffe936474251ed2afaf8f54b5ab94032","tid":1104864,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"298720b6f4d18d940c62962c13ce5d0a235172bf","tid":1104864,"uid":49302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"兩邊都係長期號輸個市...巴打唔好咁衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"巴打你啱呀，如果諗住當投資就咪買，自住係非常ok的"},{"pid":"b04c285c404e2d9be584112465965383ba595dad","tid":1104864,"uid":172861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9030ab8a6c60960a064f60c1b83ec0e9fe39848","tid":1104864,"uid":62792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"住過馬灣二年,入面無乜野食,仲要唔太好食,星期六日假期果啲全個馬灣好似旺角咁多人<br />\n平日就真係夠晒靜"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f937a4e895ca497d9400e13b0ebf692a4605851","tid":1104864,"uid":121364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fce50136300825daeba1381eeb31ed346e60320","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50adaea540dbd3bbac0139a2d7de6844187cac8a","tid":1104864,"uid":121364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"我揀深井<br />\n住咗浪翠園四五年，開頭租一期，之後上車買咗四期<br />\n住咗幾年，啱啱換樓，將會搬過碧堤半島<br />\n<br />\n碧堤位置好啲，但相比浪翠園就會遇到一啲內地人住客。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:46:25.000Z","msg":"住浪翠朝早返工出荃灣會唔會上唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋大約要幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"234A 出去你預半個鐘啦"},{"pid":"da96768dce8464880b1a121d72170f042c5adba2","tid":1104864,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"深井揸車出入都好方便"},{"pid":"0fea973767d17a5c718b68d6f9f0edb7f049bcd4","tid":1104864,"uid":32213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"不要買珀麗灣<br />\n唔想呢度雜曬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7188efb4747808091852bc4bf671a63eafe3ceb4","tid":1104864,"uid":30351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:27:05.000Z","msg":"兩度都住過<br />\n馬灣就一入伙就住<br />\n2002定2003年<br />\n個時成個島得一間百佳開既便利店<br />\n同一間又一間餐室<br />\n痴線我竟然咁都生存到<br />\n<br />\n當年住實好架<br />\n$3出青衣<br />\n後來葵芳好似都係$5.x<br />\n會所係靚，不過我好少用<br />\n佢唔整呢啲邊有人入去住呀<br />\n<br />\n住左9年<br />\n搬返出深井<br />\n兩個世界啦<br />\n可以渣車生活唔同晒<br />\n<br />\n出夜街永遠有紅頂返到屋企樓下<br />\n住馬灣又要計住搭三搭九青衣車<br />\n搭正搭半葵芳車<br />\n試過叫的士佬飛車去穿巴站<br />\n要閘係穿巴車頭落先趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住馬灣唔係唔好<br />\n你返工返中環就好正<br />\n朝朝上船補眠半個鐘就到<br />\n好舒服<br />\n<br />\n但去親邊都要搭多程穿巴<br />\n我住緊個時都覺得方便架<br />\n啲車跟晒時間表<br />\n<br />\n但一住過深井<br />\n荃灣屌求撚其小巴、九巴、穿巴都返到<br />\n先知馬灣既交通係咁弱智<br />\n<br />\n車位方便<br />\n浪翠唔熟，好似要三千以上<br />\n碧堤二千頭就有<br />\n成個屋苑3000多啲伙<br />\n有2300個車位<br />\n隔離幾個屋苑啲人都係租碧堤<br />\n但其實都仲有好多位淨"},{"pid":"34c8157fe7b4eabf3e6e62e0be16f3a2e403625f","tid":1104864,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7509508f520f7845b8a9a6d4566720c386146567","tid":1104864,"uid":87555,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"馬灣以前果陣入去好少人巴士船都好平<br />\n而家真係兩個世界<br />\n又不停加價<br />\n架架車都滿<br />\n<br />\n深井上屯公又係大鑊<br />\n不過就真係得依兩個揀咪深井囉<br />\n起碼多啲嘢食丫<br />\n又唔洗比珀麗還客運揸住個春袋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"荃灣入深井梗係行下路<br />\n但假日多單車"},{"pid":"d0e8316029f256ed6d152263c0296292ec377554","tid":1104864,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fce50136300825daeba1381eeb31ed346e60320","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50adaea540dbd3bbac0139a2d7de6844187cac8a","tid":1104864,"uid":121364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"我揀深井<br />\n住咗浪翠園四五年，開頭租一期，之後上車買咗四期<br />\n住咗幾年，啱啱換樓，將會搬過碧堤半島<br />\n<br />\n碧堤位置好啲，但相比浪翠園就會遇到一啲內地人住客。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:46:25.000Z","msg":"住浪翠朝早返工出荃灣會唔會上唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋大約要幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"要睇第幾期，第四期一定上唔到，一至三期都有234a/b<br />\n<br />\n如果成日要出荃灣<br />\n其實青龍頭豪景係方便過浪翠<br />\n穿巴都密<br />\n96m站頭長期車等人<br />\n返工時間一定上滿<br />\n去到深井好彩有人落<br />\n深井既人先有得上<br />\n<br />\n浪四就算把啦<br />\n而家佢地好似想叫啲區議員幫佢爭取<br />\n搵啲96m淨係接浪四既人<br />\n所以唔建議買四期"},{"pid":"1bc82def4eab54c8178357710f3f66cb18d73319","tid":1104864,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34c8157fe7b4eabf3e6e62e0be16f3a2e403625f","tid":1104864,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7509508f520f7845b8a9a6d4566720c386146567","tid":1104864,"uid":87555,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"馬灣以前果陣入去好少人巴士船都好平<br />\n而家真係兩個世界<br />\n又不停加價<br />\n架架車都滿<br />\n<br />\n深井上屯公又係大鑊<br />\n不過就真係得依兩個揀咪深井囉<br />\n起碼多啲嘢食丫<br />\n又唔洗比珀麗還客運揸住個春袋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"荃灣入深井梗係行下路<br />\n但假日多單車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"住深井最好有車，就算係碧堤，月租都係二千幾<br />\n未試過搭巴士入"},{"pid":"111d4e21941e5fbbec38e18ad368734df22fc3bb","tid":1104864,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8868bab1d35221c647d601a8fbb472a9bffd008","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40279aba6574eb3a5f8e153122c01d12729f151e","tid":1104864,"uid":245059,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"真係要睇巴打你喺邊度返工 生活圈子<br />\n<br />\n962B 去西隧大約三至四個字 之後中環 大約半個鐘左右<br />\n<br />\n碧堤返放工時間有村巴出入荃灣  <br />\n<br />\n管理費平$1.3建呎<br />\n<br />\n食嘢就出荃灣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深井冇乜嘢食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"管理費1.3建呎咁抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想問村巴班次密唔密，出荃灣要幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"穿巴得返放工時間有<br />\n10分鐘一班<br />\n10分鐘出到荃灣<br />\n其實仲有架96c小巴"},{"pid":"84b8f7813e3c4aaaa80d6797385fb1f38a958bef","tid":1104864,"uid":30351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94feaba900e77044f46abfb7907fe412885b4cba","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25495dfd391d1d89dacedc7c217afd023980179d","tid":1104864,"uid":245059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"碧堤有單位收租 幾年前住過一排<br />\n<br />\n盡量可以答巴打疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你住落覺得好唔好住，推唔推薦人買入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"住落好好<br />\n但想升值就唔建議<br />\n樓價落後係有原因的<br />\n同埋筆直有限既<br />\n我覺行豪景搭車仲方便"},{"pid":"cf2081242d013ba87d11c098cfd6a4d4881118cd","tid":1104864,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b8f7813e3c4aaaa80d6797385fb1f38a958bef","tid":1104864,"uid":30351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94feaba900e77044f46abfb7907fe412885b4cba","tid":1104864,"uid":9976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"